replies.body:
Happy New Year everyone! <3

My New Year's resolutions are to connect with this community more, keep my grades up in school, and just overall enjoy life and take the good out of everything, and everyone instead of the bad. :)

Since we're here, and it's been a rough year for Avicus, with many retirements, demotions, and bans. Everything I see on any social media site I go on it talking about how terrible 2016 was, and although 2016 was a pretty rough year there's a lot of good to take from it as well. Throughout the year we've updated to Atlas, which was really bad at first, and there are still some things that need to be fixed, overall the Atlas update was a huge step up for Avicus.

I've played on a lot of servers, and I've never seen one with such an amazing community. We have our problems, the people that don't like each other for whatever reason, but that's what holds us together. Without the community being as strong and amazing as it is on Avicus I would have left a long time ago. You guys don't realize it, but whether you are active, or inactive, or only talk to a few people, you are part of this community. 

My favorite thing about Avicus is the fact that even when we have 40-50 players on a good day, we all stick together and we do complain about a lot, but we still help in any way we can to keep Avicus alive, and improve it. I've seen many suggestions that are very good get better because of the communities ideas and constructive criticism, Let's keep that up. Help improve Avicus instead of complaining about everything we see wrong. Find a way to fix it, give ideas, be open to new ideas, and even if your suggestion seems stupid, suggest it, the community can help you improve it.

Thanks to a few people. :)

{tag=d78324b1575744218df3c1eeaffe7489} : You've been one of my good friends for a long time now, and it's always fun talking to you about random crap that neither one of us are actually interested in. xD

{tag=99b8a2a4cb224ba1a6837cd90a02aac5} : When I became Junior Mod, and slightly before, you were the first one to really try to talk to me and spend time with me. I had Mods and Seniors as friends before, but you were the first to really talk to me consistently.

{tag=fbd4b4d461864581b408666bb8a12df4} and {tag=2a2d50b3fb24420ca526f46eaeca52ff} (Ashley and Isaac): You two are cute. ;) I really hate your names most of the time though. xD Anyway, you both have been friends for a long time, it's been great. :)

{tag=b5c1ef1ef41a4124b6dbe72a84d9495f} : We don't talk a lot but you were my first friend on Avicus/MCZone. Nearly 4 years ago. That's honestly insane that it's been that long. It's crazy to think that I've known you and many Walls players for 3+ years. 

{tag=534988e41992448ab9b41316ea0d53ac} : Nia... We didn't even really talk until like a month ago, but since then you've helped me with 3 different problems, so thank you. Also- k. <3

I'm way too lazy to list everyone, so...:

Walls players: It's been a rough year for Walls. xD It may not come back soon, but if nothing else we've all made some really good friends playing Walls, It's been a great year, thank you all. <3 :)

DTM/Nebula players: I'm still pretty new to DTM but you guys are very welcoming. Thanks for a great year, and I hope there's another great year to come. <3

Staff team: It's only been a short time so far, but it;s been really fun, and I've made a lot of new friends since I've joined. Thank you guys for helping keep the server alive, with whatever you do. <3 <3

Avicus community: Don't change. Keep being the amazing people that you are, and keep welcoming new players, and get to know them! One of the best things that Avicus has right now, is you guys. Keep it up! :D <333

Thank you everyone for a great year, and I hope 2017 can be even better! Good luck to everyone on your New Year's resolutions and Happy New years!

-LiloOe/Micah.

Happy New Year everyone! <3

My New Year's resolutions are to connect with this community more, keep my grades up in school, and just overall enjoy life and take the good out of everything, and everyone instead of the bad. :)

Since we're here, and it's been a rough year for Avicus, with many retirements, demotions, and bans. Oh 2016.....
You've brung amazing, weird, and devasting things as a whole. You've brought memories and friends that came here and there. Without 2016...I wouldn't be able to thank:...
Everyone:
All of you had an impact on me in a way. I would thank you personally, but it would be a reallly, really, really long post, so sorry. Thank you to the community on suggesting ideas and to the developers for implementing them. Thank you to the Officials for creating fun tournaments and to the Refs for reffing it and the Medias for streaming. Thank you Map Developers for developing maps and working with Builders to build maps. Thank you builders for building amazing maps. Thank you Junior Moderators, Moderators, Senior Moderators, and Admins for things you do towards the server and staff team. Thank you to the retired/demoted for the service they provided. Finally, and not least, thank you to the Social Media for advertising this wonderful server :3. I can't wait to see what 2017 brings us.

{tag=a9f11454beac4cc3a1381780802c8794}: Great friend, glad you are Senior because you deserve it. I liked the times when we would chat on skype and once I got Jr, I was so happy to be Staff eith you. Thanks for everything!
{tag=fbd4b4d461864581b408666bb8a12df4}: Thanks to you, your brother, and {tag=3ed3b5a8573b43a59405cb4e53ce023a}, I learned different things. I started to find ways to improve myself from the shit you gave me xD.
{tag=0b8f95fa0f404f289fd0b8e243bb6800}: Honestly, I would of never have improved my denial reasons back in April, if I didn't talk to you in game about how I could improve. Thanks for that <3
{tag=a349582f6eff4f53ad88aec5dfce01fb}: When I joined Endless, you became a good friend of mine. We would play Avicus together, skywars, or UHC SG, and they were fun times. I feel that since I became Staff, we have been departing to our own ways and I hope to change that.
{tag=3feb57900603446c9bbfd5fb40759f41}: Thank you for accepting me to Endless Aptitude (Team Rocket for those who do not know) and for being an awesome leader. Your team was my first competitve experience and I appreciate it :).

You are a great friend and great person to talk to. However, when you got Mentor, you seemed to be a control freak, but I realized you were trying to fix our mistakes as a team and I appreciate you for what you did.
{tag=bff56e079469477281be84fc627ea113}: You are a great friend to talk to and to meme with :3. Thank you for referring me and seeing potential in me as a Staff Member. I hope to see great things happen to you in the future :D. I love our conversations that we have in TS xD.

Btw {tag=3902b25efd6544a78b55be7652694f39} I'm sorry for the false bans this year, hopefully it won't happen again in 2017 >.<.
